<dl id="n06157q"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06157q">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06157q"> 157(q)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ye do show the L&apos;s death</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[from THE SACRAMENT OF THE LORD&apos;S SUPPER]</font> &ldquo;A THANKFUL REMEMBRANCE OF HIS DEATH.&rdquo;&mdash;&ldquo;For as often as ye eat this bread, and drink this cup, <mark>ye do show the LORD&apos;s death</mark> till he come.&rdquo; <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 57</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
